<p>Note that the <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mtext mathvariant="monospace">crs,</mtext><mtext> </mtext><mtext mathvariant="monospace">wit,</mtext><mtext> </mtext><mtext mathvariant="monospace">stmt</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\texttt{crs, wit, stmt}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.75em;vertical-align:-0.13889em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord texttt">crs, wit, stmt</span></span></span></span></span> remain unchanged for Bulletproofs+.</p>

<h3 id="bulletproofs-verification">Bulletproofs Verification</h3>

<p>Given an aggregated BP proof, a verifier needs to check the following:
<span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mtable width="100%"><mtr><mtd width="50%"></mtd><mtd><mrow><msup><mi>g</mi><mover accent="true"><mi>t</mi><mo>^</mo></mover></msup><mo>⋅</mo><msup><mi>h</mi><mi>τ</mi></msup><mo><mover><mo><mo>=</mo></mo><mo stretchy="false" lspace="0em" rspace="0em">?</mo></mover></mo><msup><mi>g</mi><mrow><mi>δ</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>y</mi><mo separator="true">,</mo><mi>z</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></msup><mo>⋅</mo><msup><mtext mathvariant="bold">V</mtext><mrow><msup><mi>z</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>⋅</mo><msup><mtext mathvariant="bold">z</mtext><mi>m</mi></msup></mrow></msup><mo>⋅</mo><msubsup><mi>T</mi><mn>1</mn><mi>x</mi></msubsup><mo>⋅</mo><msubsup><mi>T</mi><mn>2</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></msubsup></mrow></mtd><mtd width="50%"></mtd><mtd><mtext>(1)</mtext></mtd></mtr></mtable><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
\tag{1} 
g^{\hat{t}} \cdot h^{\tau} \stackrel{?}{=} g^{\delta(y,z)} \cdot \textbf{V}^{z^2 \cdot \textbf{z}^m} \cdot T_1^x \cdot T_2^{x^2}
</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1.2224039999999998em;vertical-align:-0.19444em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">g</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:1.0279639999999999em;"><span style="top:-3.113em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord accent mtight"><span class="vlist-t"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.87852em;"><span style="top:-2.7em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">t</span></span></span><span style="top:-2.88408em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="accent-body" style="left:-0.16666em;"><span class="mord mtight">^</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span><span class="mbin">⋅</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1.152978em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathdefault">h</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.7143919999999999em;"><span style="top:-3.113em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight" style="margin-right:0.1132em;">τ</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel"><span class="mop op-limits"><span c