Note that the verifier can compute <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>P</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">P</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.13889em;">P</span></span></span></span> as</p>

<p><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mtable width="100%"><mtr><mtd width="50%"></mtd><mtd><mrow><mi>P</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>A</mi><mo>⋅</mo><msup><mi>S</mi><mi>x</mi></msup><mo>⋅</mo><msup><mtext mathvariant="bold">g</mtext><mrow><mo>−</mo><mi>z</mi><mo>⋅</mo><msup><mtext mathvariant="bold">1</mtext><mrow><mi>m</mi><mi>n</mi></mrow></msup></mrow></msup><mo>⋅</mo><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><msup><mtext mathvariant="bold">h</mtext><mo mathvariant="normal" lspace="0em" rspace="0em">′</mo></msup><msup><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mrow><mi>z</mi><mo>⋅</mo><msup><mtext mathvariant="bold">y</mtext><mrow><mi>m</mi><mi>n</mi></mrow></msup><mo>+</mo><mtext mathvariant="bold">d</mtext></mrow></msup></mrow></mtd><mtd width="50%"></mtd><mtd><mtext>(3)</mtext></mtd></mtr></mtable><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\tag{3} P = A \cdot S^x \cdot \textbf{g}^{-z \cdot \textbf{1}^{mn}} \cdot (\textbf{h}&#x27;)^{z \cdot \textbf{y}^{mn} + \textbf{d}}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.13889em;">P</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">A</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span><span class="mbin">⋅</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.7143919999999999em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.05764em;">S</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="