"mclose">)</span></span></span></span> to get a single inner product proof check, we get</p>

<p><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msup><mtext mathvariant="bold">g</mtext><mrow><mi>a</mi><mo>⋅</mo><mtext mathvariant="bold">s</mtext></mrow></msup><mo>⋅</mo><msup><mtext mathvariant="bold">h</mtext><mrow><mi>b</mi><mo>⋅</mo><msup><mtext mathvariant="bold">s</mtext><mo mathvariant="normal" lspace="0em" rspace="0em">′</mo></msup></mrow></msup><mo>⋅</mo><msup><mi>g</mi><mrow><msub><mi>x</mi><mi>u</mi></msub><mo>⋅</mo><mi>a</mi><mi>b</mi></mrow></msup><mo><mover><mo><mo>=</mo></mo><mo stretchy="false" lspace="0em" rspace="0em">?</mo></mover></mo><mrow><mo fence="true">(</mo><mi>A</mi><mo>⋅</mo><msup><mi>S</mi><mi>x</mi></msup><mo>⋅</mo><msup><mtext mathvariant="bold">g</mtext><mrow><mo>−</mo><mi>z</mi><mo>⋅</mo><msup><mtext mathvariant="bold">1</mtext><mrow><mi>m</mi><mi>n</mi></mrow></msup></mrow></msup><mo>⋅</mo><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><msup><mtext mathvariant="bold">h</mtext><mo mathvariant="normal" lspace="0em" rspace="0em">′</mo></msup><msup><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mrow><mi>z</mi><mo>⋅</mo><msup><mtext mathvariant="bold">y</mtext><mrow><mi>m</mi><mi>n</mi></mrow></msup><mo>+</mo><mtext mathvariant="bold">d</mtext></mrow></msup><mo>⋅</mo><msup><mi>h</mi><mrow><mo>−</mo><mi>μ</mi></mrow></msup><mo>⋅</mo><msup><mi>g</mi><mrow><msub><mi>x</mi><mi>u</mi></msub><mo>⋅</mo><mover accent="true"><mi>t</mi><mo>^</mo></mover></mrow></msup><mo fence="true">)</mo></mrow><mo>⋅</mo><munderover><mo>∏</mo><mrow><mi>j</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mrow><msub><mtext>log</mtext><mn>2</mn></msub><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>n</mi><mi>m</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></munderover><msubsup><mi>L</mi><mi>j</mi><msubsup><mi>x</mi><mi>j</mi><mn>2</mn></msubsup></msubsup><mo>⋅</mo><msubsup><mi>R</mi><mi>j</mi><msubsup><mi>x</mi><mi>j</mi><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></msubsup></msubsup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
\textbf{g}^{a \cdot \textbf{s}} \cdot \textbf{h}^{b \cdot \textbf{s}&#x27;} \cdot g^{x_u \cdot ab} \stackrel{?}{=} 
\left(
    A \cdot S^x \cdot \textbf{g}^{-z \cdot \textbf{1}^{mn}} \cdot (\textbf{h}&#x27;)^{z \cdot \textbf{y}^{mn} + \textbf{d}} \cdot h^{-\mu} \cdot g^{x_u \cdot \hat{t}}
\right) 
\cdot \prod_{j=1}^{\text{log}_2(nm)} L_j^{x_j^2} \cdot R_j^{x_j^{-2}}
</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.918555em;vertical-align:-0.19444em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord text"><span class="mord textbf">g</span></span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.724115em;"><span style="top:-3.113em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">a</span><span class="mbin mtight">⋅</span><span class="mord text mtight"><span class="mord textbf mtight">s</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span><span class="mbin">⋅</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1.0268199999999998em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord text"><span class="mord textbf">h</span></span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:1.0268199999999998em;"><span style="top:-3.1473400000000002em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">b</span><span class="mbin mtight">⋅</span><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord text mtight"><span class="mord textbf mtight">s</span></span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.8278285714285715em;"><span style="top:-2.931em;margin-right:0.07142857142857144em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.5em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size3 size1 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mtight">′</span></span></span></span></span></span></span