<p>By substituting <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mover accent="true"><mi>A</mi><mo>^</mo></mover></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\hat{A}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.9467699999999999em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord accent"><span class="vlist-t"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.9467699999999999em;"><span style="top:-3em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathdefault">A</span></span></span><span style="top:-3.25233em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="accent-body" style="left:-0.11110999999999999em;"><span class="mord">^</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>, the verification boils downs to a single multi-exponentiation check.</p>

<p><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msup><mtext mathvariant="bold">g</mtext><mrow><mi>e</mi><mo>⋅</mo><msup><mi>r</mi><mo mathvariant="normal" lspace="0em" rspace="0em">′</mo></msup><mo>⋅</mo><mtext mathvariant="bold">s</mtext></mrow></msup><mo>⋅</mo><msup><mtext mathvariant="bold">h</mtext><mrow><mi>e</mi><mo>⋅</mo><msup><mi>s</mi><mo mathvariant="normal" lspace="0em" rspace="0em">′</mo></msup><mo>⋅</mo><msup><mtext mathvariant="bold">s</mtext><mo mathvariant="normal" lspace="0em" rspace="0em">′</mo></msup></mrow></msup><mo>⋅</mo><msup><mi>g</mi><mrow><msup><mi>r</mi><mo mathvariant="normal" lspace="0em" rspace="0em">′</mo></msup><mo>⊙</mo><msup><mi>s</mi><mo mathvariant="normal" lspace="0em" rspace="0em">′</mo></msup></mrow></msup><mo>⋅</mo><msup><mi>h</mi><msup><mi>δ</mi><mo mathvariant="normal" lspace="0em" rspace="0em">′</mo></msup></msup><mo><mover><mo><mo>=</mo></mo><mo stretchy="false" lspace="0em" rspace="0em">?</mo></mover></mo><msup><mrow><mo fence="true">(</mo><mi>A</mi><mo>⋅</mo><msup><mtext mathvariant="bold">g</mtext><mrow><mo>−</mo><mi>z</mi><mo>⋅</mo><msup><mtext mathvariant="bold">1</mtext><mrow><mi>m</mi><mi>n</mi></mrow></msup></mrow></msup><mo>⋅</mo><msup><mtext mathvariant="bold">h</mtext><mrow><mi>z</mi><mo>⋅</mo><msup><mtext mathvariant="bold">1</mtext><mrow><mi>m</mi><mi>n</mi></mrow></msup><mo>+</mo><mtext mathvariant="bold">d</mtext><mo>∘</mo><msup><mover accent="true"><mi>y</mi><mo stretchy="true">←</mo></mover><mrow><mi>m</mi><mi>n</mi></mrow></msup></mrow></msup><mo>⋅</mo><msup><mtext mathvariant="bold">V</mtext><mrow><msup><mi>y</mi><mrow><mi>m</mi><mi>n</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mo>⋅</mo><msup><mi>z</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>⋅</mo><msup><mtext mathvariant="bold">z</mtext><mi>m</mi></msup></mrow></msup><mo>⋅</mo><msup><mi>g</mi><mrow><mi>ζ</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>y</mi><mo separator="true">,</mo><mi>z</mi>